Dogs are the best🥰 Cats are the best too! But dogs… dogs are a special type of Gift in this life. They don’t care what happened, they don’t care who promised what or if you didn’t show up as your best self. They truly don’t judge. They just want pets, smooches, cuddles and snacks. They don’t hold onto the bad stuff. And if you cry they really really want you to stop. And give them pets. And to share a snack with them🥲 We are so lucky we get to have dogs😍🐕🤗 I am so lucky to be your Mom, Teddy💗💗💗

Can’t wait to share this story with you all!🎃

elevAtion Aerial presents-
🖤80’s WITCH HUNT🖤
Join us for a night of Witchy Tiki fun in the Speakeasy Room at @tongahut, LA’s oldest Tiki bar! 
The beautiful witches of @elevationaerialdance will wow and thrill you with spooky and delicious burlesque performances while you sip on delightfully devilish custom Tiki cocktails.
Your ticket includes one general admission seat, one custom cocktail poured from the sky by the elevAtion Aerial bartenders, a souvenir Tonga Hut cup for you to keep, and reserved seating in the Tonga Hut outside lounge after the show.

Two shows - 7 p.m. and 9 p.m. VIP Tables also available🖤
